bn Sa\u2019d reported: We were in the trench with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while he was digging and we were carrying the dirt away. The Prophet passed by us and he said, \u201cO Allah, there is no life worth living but the life\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24733,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/04\/24\/no-true-life-but-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":3026,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Akhirah: No true life but the Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 24, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, there is no life worth living but the life of the Hereafter, so be generous to the Ansar and the Muhajirun.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3796, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1805 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14882,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/eat-blessed-suhur\/","url_meta":{"origin":3026,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Suhur: Blessings in pre-fasting morning meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTake the pre-fasting meal, for surely there are blessings in the pre-fasting meal.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1923, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1095 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8161,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/14\/blackseed-cure-except-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":3026,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Healing properties of blackseed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"This blackseed is healing for all diseases but poison.\u201d She said, \u201cWhat is poison?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cDeath.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5363 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0627\u0626\u0634\u0629 \u0642\u0627\u0644\u062a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37913,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/23\/two-meals-a-day\/","url_meta":{"origin":3026,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Meals: The Prophet ate a portion of dates every day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 23, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The household of Muhammad, peace and blessings be upon him, never ate two meals in a day but that one of them consisted of dates. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6455 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0644\u064e \u0622\u0644\u064f \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0651\u062f\u064d \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18999,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/06\/hijamah-cupping-honey\/","url_meta":{"origin":3026,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Hijamah: There is healing in cupping, honey","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 6, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is healing in three: a cupping operation, a drink of honey, and cauterization with fire, but I forbid my nation from using cauterization.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5357 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u062